This project is intended to test a rest api that performs gets and returns users and albums. It can return all users and all albums or individual user and individual album.

The rest api can be accessed through this address: https://my-json-server.typicode.com/seplusi/rest/

To get all albums:
https://my-json-server.typicode.com/seplusi/rest/albums

to get individual album:
https://my-json-server.typicode.com/seplusi/rest/albums/#

To get all users:
https://my-json-server.typicode.com/seplusi/rest/users

To get individual users:
https://my-json-server.typicode.com/seplusi/rest/users/#

This project contains the following files:
db.json       : rest API source code
test_case.py  : Python file with test cases

How to execute test cases:
1) Install python3
2) python3 ./test_case.py

Execution result:

python3 ./test_case.py -v
test_get_all_albums (__main__.TestPostitWebApplication) ... ok
test_get_all_users (__main__.TestPostitWebApplication) ... ok
test_get_individual_album (__main__.TestPostitWebApplication) ... ok
test_get_individual_user (__main__.TestPostitWebApplication) ... ok

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Ran 4 tests in 0.914s

